OL,3,CTeenage girl tells court school stab
OL,4,Cattack 'doesn't sound like me'
OL,6,FA 14-year-old girl accused of the
OL,7,Fattempted murder of two teachers and a
OL,8,Fpupil during a school knife attack in
OL,9,FAmmanford has told a court she "can't
OL,10,Fremember" why she carried out the
OL,11,Fstabbings.
OL,13,FThe teenage girl admits to intending
OL,14,Fto wound two teachers and a pupil and
OL,15,Falso carrying a bladed article on
OL,16,Fschool premises.
OL,18,FHowever, she denies that she attempted
OL,19,Fto murder them during the attack at
OL,20,FYsgol Dyffryn Aman in April last year.
