OL,3,CTeenage girl tells court school stab
OL,4,Cattack 'doesn't sound like me'
OL,6,FTeachers Fiona Elias, Liz Hopkin and a
OL,7,Fpupil all suffered multiple stab
OL,8,Fwounds.
OL,10,FTaking questions from her defence
OL,11,Fbarrister, the girl told a jury she
OL,12,Fhad carried a knife to school since
OL,13,Fthe age of 12 after feeling "anxious
OL,14,Fand scared" due to bullying.
OL,16,FThe teenager said she kept a knife
OL,17,Fwith her "every day," but said she
OL,18,Fused the knife to harm herself.
