OL,6,FThe court was told that in September
OL,7,F2023, teacher Fiona Elias found a
OL,8,Fkitchen knife in the defendant's bag
OL,9,Fafter a search.
OL,11,FThe girl was suspended for around a
OL,12,Fweek and her father agreed to check
OL,13,Fher school bag each morning for knives
OL,14,Fas a condition of his daughter being
OL,15,Fallowed back to Ysgol Dyffryn Aman.
OL,17,FAsked why she took a knife to school
OL,18,Fthat day, the girl replied, "I truly
OL,19,Fdon't remember at this point in time."
