OL,6,FThe girl was then questioned about the
OL,7,Fattacks on Ms Elias, Ms Hopkin, and
OL,8,Fthe pupil.
OL,10,F"Are you sorry?" she was asked.
OL,12,F"Yes," she replied.
OL,14,F"If you could go back, would you
OL,15,Fchange things?"
OL,17,F"Yeah," she replied.
OL,19,F"How do you feel knowing you caused
OL,20,Fserious injuries to the victims?"
