OL,6,F"It doesn't sound like me," the
OL,7,Fdefendant said.
OL,9,FDuring her evidence, the teenager
OL,10,Fdenied wanting to kill Ms Elias, Ms
OL,11,FHopkin, and the pupil.
OL,13,FWhen questioned about her recollection
OL,14,Fof the attacks, the girl replied she
OL,15,Fcouldn't remember.
OL,17,FDuring cross-examination, it was put
OL,18,Fto the defendant that she set out to
OL,19,Fkill Ms Elias.
