OL,6,F"Having opened the knife and locked it
OL,7,Fwith the blade open you attacked Ms
OL,8,FElias and said, 'I'm going to kill
OL,9,Fyou'," the prosecution said.
OL,11,F"I don't remember, I don't remember
OL,12,Fhearing anything at the time," the
OL,13,Fgirl replied.
OL,15,F"You made three stabbing gestures and
OL,16,Fkicked out?"
OL,18,F"I don't remember doing it," the girl
OL,19,Fsaid.
