OL,6,F"I suggest you wanted to kill Ms
OL,7,FElias?" the prosecution put to the
OL,8,Fgirl.
OL,10,F"No," she replied.
OL,12,FJudge Paul Thomas KC then addressed
OL,13,Fthe jury reminding them of the law
OL,14,Fthey needed to consider when reaching
OL,15,Ftheir verdicts.
OL,17,FHe also asked them to consider the age
OL,18,Fof the teenage defendant and the nine
OL,19,Fmonths that had passed since the
OL,20,Fattack when assessing her evidence.
